<div class="video-examples-header">
<a href="#feedback" class="font-s float-right text-blue" data-modal-target="login">Feedback</a>
<h3 class="bold">Video Example(s):</h3>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-featured">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="2jy9el" data-video-descrip="In Season 1 &amp;quot;Hat Luncheon&amp;quot;, Owen is so nervous about giving his speech at the Hat Luncheon that he sweats through his formal shirts and he changed his shirt three times." data-video-title="Changed Shirts Three Times" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/2jy9el_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/cp_i_changed_shirts_three_times.png" data-video-trope="Main/OverlyNervousFlopSweat" data-video-tropename="Overly Nervous Flop Sweat" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="5.00" data-video-rating-count="1" data-video-media-sources="Recap/CentralParkS1E3HatLuncheon,WesternAnimation/CentralPark" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
<div class="featured-widget-vid-iframe">
<video id='featured-video-player' class='video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-16-9' controls data-setup='{"ga": {"eventsToTrack": ["error"]}}'>
</video>
</div>
</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Changed Shirts Three Times</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In Season 1 &quot;Hat Luncheon&quot;, Owen is so nervous about giving his speech at the Hat Luncheon that he sweats through his formal shirts and he changed his shirt three times. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="square_ad footer-article-ad main_2" data-isolated="0"></div>
